{"tid":907743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賓總：退休後想到中國買地居住","createTime":"2018-11-19T04:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T05:00:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"542f560ad05a9cae94f11a9bc397c0a264d4eaed","tid":907743,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2210000/2211513/1119002_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2210000%2F2211513%2F1119002_1024.jpg&h=d00838de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平正在文萊國事訪問，明日將轉抵菲律賓展開兩天國事訪問。在習近平抵達前，菲律賓總統杜特爾特接受內地傳媒等訪問時稱，菲中關係目前處於高峰，他與習近平關係非常友好融洽，將爭取讓小女兒向習獻唱一首中文歌。他又透露，希望退休後有機會去中國居住。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特表示，菲中關係曾一度陷入低谷，他兩年前就任總統後，在雙方共同努力下，兩國關係重回友好合作的正軌，目前中國已成為菲律賓最大貿易夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，菲中關係目前處於高峰，形容是「盛開的繁花」，相信習近平此行將會把兩國關係提升到全新高度，全面深化兩國在各領域合作，包括商討如何在「一帶一路」框架下合作，將更多設想付諸行動。<br />\n<br />\n對於兩國一些分歧，特別是圍繞南海問題，他希望通過協商與對話的方式來解決。<br />\n<br />\n爭取讓細女用中文與習交流<br />\n<br />\n此外，杜特爾特透露，他的小女兒剛滿14歲，正在學習中文，他會爭取讓小女兒用中文與習近平交流，或獻唱一首中文歌。<br />\n<br />\n他又透露，自己外公來自中國，如果中國政府允許，他甚至打算在中國買地建屋，「我想跟外公一樣在中國居住，為退休做準備，等我老了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2211513/%E7%BF%92%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%B2%E5%89%8D%20%E6%9D%9C%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E7%89%B9%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%BE%8C%E6%83%B3%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%B7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2211513%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%2520%25E6%259D%259C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%2589%25B9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25BD%258F%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=slPm1AumRY3DDxQ8WmMjY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0ddf5ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2211513/%E7%BF%92%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%B2%E5%89%8D%20%E6%9D%9C%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E7%89%B9%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%BE%8C%E6%83%B3%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%B7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F?mtc=20023</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTp3i_BYHOaoIzEnKbNCrwf_12Auo3B2shiJKzuP_8vH_Z-xfHp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTp3i_BYHOaoIzEnKbNCrwf_12Auo3B2shiJKzuP_8vH_Z-xfHp&h=1c0ce085&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c7dd498c6ab37306ce899615084ae1f3b907202","tid":907743,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.boxun.com/news/images/2015/12/201512310706china1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boxun.com%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F2015%2F12%2F201512310706china1.gif&h=5e3eced0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}